  <li>Is there a part of Jesusâ€™ ministry or life that you have a hard time believing or comprehending?</li>
  <li>What stood out to you about Craigâ€™s defense of the resurrection of Christ?</li>
  <li>How is your changed life a miracle? Tell your story.</li>
